{"tid":1890312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網上號召今午為染疫警「獻花打氣」 惟至中午仍未見有人在醫院大堂聚集","createTime":"2020-02-21T06:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T07:33:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"27f53bf61d424097b2d774c266639ab3857576fb","tid":1890312,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"本港的新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診個案累計共68宗，當中包括一名駐守北角警署的48歲防暴警。有關警員在位於觀塘的聯合醫院接受隔離治療。<br />\n<br />\n網上有人發起支持活動，呼籲參加者今明兩日中午到聯合醫院獻花打氣。不過中午時分，未見有人在醫院大堂聚集。<br />\n<br />\n針對以上的網上號召，醫院管理局早上提醒市民，公立醫院已啟動緊急應變級別，全面禁止探訪。基於公眾衛生考慮，醫管局呼籲市民不應前往公立醫院聚集，以免引起散播傳染病的風險。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1706044/</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef9f6b93d25af1095c133d4e7159db7227c4035","tid":1890312,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150fb2139a4dedfb5085b689c9ae4633cf36fd07","tid":1890312,"uid":70195,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:30:06.000Z","msg":"藍屍一向得把口 冇錢邊個去"},{"pid":"03e1d793a59bc868af9ce4373106a85d673f456e","tid":1890312,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33939a2d9a21f022816ef4cb63a96a14ba6ff375","tid":1890312,"uid":44646,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2402bcf1bdad11b7a8298744f90b067797464a","tid":1890312,"uid":256783,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:31:25.000Z